{
  "ComponentID": "RT8096C",
  "ComponentType": "Synchronous Step-Down DC/DC Converter (Buck Converter)",
  "Description": "The RT8096C is a high-efficiency, 1A output current, synchronous step-down DC/DC converter using a Current Mode Constant-On-Time (CMCOT) control architecture. It operates from a 2.5V to 6V input and provides an adjustable output voltage from 0.6V to 3.4V. It integrates both high-side and low-side power switches, requires minimal external components, and includes features such as soft-start, power-good indicator (6-pin version), cycle-by-cycle over-current protection, output under-voltage protection, input under-voltage lockout, thermal shutdown, and light-load power-saving mode.",
